&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;네트워크 현대화&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
